{
  "stem": "15577.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were left only-- it was left only a group of a hundred or something people which were called liquidation comando.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Among them is-- was this cousin doctor who is today's brother-in-law of mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were sent-- all the men were sent to a camp which, which its name was Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All the women-- and were thousands-- were sent-- were sent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We spent there 10 days, which were terrible 10 days-- terrible because of the circumstance and terrible because of the conditions, terrible because of the approach to us by the Polish inmates who were sitting there as prisoners because of being murderers, thieves, and so on, and because of not getting food, because of being squeezed in, in places where 50 people had space enough to stay and we were 500 or 600.",
      "word_count": 77
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So imagine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it, it stopped being terrible in the movement after six days, or five days, or seven days, a few days, when we knew that there is a list which each will be respected-- because we were among all these thousands who were sent away from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we didn't know how it-- how it would be fulfilled, the so-called list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After a few days, they put us in a special barrack that means we were separated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At that moment, we knew that we belonged to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly, but I think around 10 days, two weeks, when he stayed in Gross Rosen, we have been transported to, to Czech, to Sudety, Sudetes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And to so-called Brnenec.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The place was called Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We-- I am speaking about the 800 men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "By the way, the others, the thousands-- [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
